  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1271920/extras/8522204d319a95044dcbc927dacb8130.poster.avif?t=1677251172\" width=600 height=118 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1271920/extras/8522204d319a95044dcbc927dacb8130.webm?t=1677251172\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Take command and lead your troops on a turn-based war full of <strong>Strategy and Tanks.</strong></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unlock up to <strong>97 Officers and Commanders</strong>, each one with their own Special Power and sexy style.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>More than 40 Hours of gameplay</strong> in tons of missions on Campaign Mode: Winter's Blood, Eastern Coalition, Free Nations and UDF factions will battle for the final Victory.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1271920/extras/4774ec095dbd9cadfeb12bfc75fd8857.poster.avif?t=1677251172\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1271920/extras/4774ec095dbd9cadfeb12bfc75fd8857.webm?t=1677251172\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1271920/extras/4774ec095dbd9cadfeb12bfc75fd8857.mp4?t=1677251172\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1271920/extras/da7a1e58f73bf07b3fa96c2bb82886c7.poster.avif?t=1677251172\" width=600 height=118 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1271920/extras/da7a1e58f73bf07b3fa96c2bb82886c7.webm?t=1677251172\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Your army is comprised of the toughest and the most stunning female Captains, Lieutenants, and Sergeants. Ready to fight under your command, their loyalty increases as you win battles. Rank them up to develop their skills, and take them to new heights. Then construct your ultimate battle deck! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1271920/extras/1d9edda86eee5d140d333f6ed2995450.poster.avif?t=1677251172\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1271920/extras/1d9edda86eee5d140d333f6ed2995450.webm?t=1677251172\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1271920/extras/1d9edda86eee5d140d333f6ed2995450.mp4?t=1677251172\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1271920/extras/5d9f1d0aa12fe73bcece20bccd8225b3.poster.avif?t=1677251172\" width=600 height=118 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1271920/extras/5d9f1d0aa12fe73bcece20bccd8225b3.webm?t=1677251172\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Take command of up to 14 troop types including a wide range of military forces, from Rocket Artillery and Motorbikes to Bombers and Helicopters. All your troops have unique abilities and level up the more they fight.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1271920/extras/27e2855ef67505578ed6a46f11a53737.poster.avif?t=1677251172\" width=620 height=116 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1271920/extras/27e2855ef67505578ed6a46f11a53737.webm?t=1677251172\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1271920/extras/27e2855ef67505578ed6a46f11a53737.mp4?t=1677251172\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1271920/extras/802cc24547eccf296cfd903b0192ce45.poster.avif?t=1677251172\" width=600 height=118 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1271920/extras/802cc24547eccf296cfd903b0192ce45.webm?t=1677251172\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Angels On Tanks conflict shifts when the army of Winter’s Blood are power hungry and have a devious plan for the newly discovered super powerful Crystals that can create an indestructible army. Take to the battlefield and use advanced war strategies, weapons, and tactics to decimate your opponent.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1271920/extras/82dfd48aeb637979077d7b58087c42ed.poster.avif?t=1677251172\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1271920/extras/82dfd48aeb637979077d7b58087c42ed.webm?t=1677251172\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1271920/extras/82dfd48aeb637979077d7b58087c42ed.mp4?t=1677251172\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
